name: OSLogMessageComponent.Argument
desc: An object representing data that corresponds to an argument in a message payload.

items.name: case data(Data)
items.desc: A data object returned by the OSLog API that corresponds to the argument.

items.name: case double(Double)
items.desc: A double returned by the OSLog API that corresponds to the argument.

items.name: case signed(Int64)
items.desc: A signed 64-bit integer returned by the OSLog API that corresponds to the argument.

items.name: case string(String)
items.desc: A string returned by the OSLog API that corresponds to the argument.

items.name: case undefined
items.desc: A undefined object returned by the OSLog API that corresponds to the argument.

items.name: case unsigned(UInt64)
items.desc: An unsigned 64-bit integer returned by the OSLog API that corresponds to the argument.
